message.body: Hey! Do we need a reservation for volver on Thursday? Or did you cover that?
Or is this go in and hang out? Lol I'm confused.
I thought it was going to be more along the let's go and hang out since we were doing the Jazz thing. They have the happy hour menu at that time but I you want more of dinner we could do that too,
Oh no I was just wondering. They only have tasting menus so I didn't know what the plan was lol
Yeh that's too much food Haha let's shoot for the bar
Okay perfect. I'm excited :) are you working today?
Boo! They gave us off. I won't complain but it's not bad
Yeh, perks of following the school district :) but I'm doing homework if that makes you feel better haha
Thanks Haha I need to be productive
